data.description: 'CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS' Why wait on new construction? Come check-out this lovely move-in ready full-brick beauty in Titus Park Phase 1. This spacious single-story home has 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths and 1 half bath. Its open floor plan offers formal dining and a generous gathering room, perfect for entertaining. There's also a casual breakfast area included in the open concept kitchen, granite countertops, oversized island that comfortably seats 4, and a contemporary decorative backsplash. The kitchen has plenty of storage with a large corner pantry and ample cabinet space including beneath the Island. This awesome home has 9-foot tray ceilings in the dining room, bonus room, and master bedroom. Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, with carpet only in bedrooms, ceiling fans in all bedrooms, gathering room and flex/bonus room. The spacious 3rd and 4th bedrooms share a Jack and Jill bathroom for privacy and plenty of room with a double sink vanity, perfect for guests. 2nd bedroom is a large bedroom with an ensuite bathroom and closet with a large flex/bonus room attached, great for a private office or extended stay for guests to have their own living space. Main bedroom is a luxurious size that could even accommodate a small sitting area, it also has a huge walk-in closet, double sinks in the bathroom, garden tub and separate shower. All appliances are included: stainless steel side by side refrigerator, dishwasher, oven, stove, microwave, LG washer and LG dryer. Upgraded comfort toilets, upgraded interior paint. A full 3 car garage with loads of space for vehicles, golf cart and/or extra storage. Covered and screened lanai, privacy fenced backyard, security cameras, alarm system, water softener, irrigation system and added gutters. All window treatments convey. To top it off, this home comes with an Old Republic home warranty (valid until Jan 2026) which will be transferred to the new owner. Short commute to Tyndall Air Force Base, shopping, restaurants, and schools. Make an appointment to view this amazing home today! You must see it in person to fully appreciate all the wonderful features it offers. All measurements are approximate and should be verified by the purchaser.
